text: Tserendonoin Sanjaa (born 7 November 1936) is a Mongolian wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle heavyweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:Mongolian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Mongolia Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
